org.hibernate.query.criteria

Interface JpaQueryStructure<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JpaCriteriaNode, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SqmQuerySpec

    public interface JpaQueryStructure<T>
extends JpaCriteriaNode
    Models a SELECT query. Used as a delegate in implementing CriteriaQuery and Subquery.
    See Also:
    JpaCriteriaQuery, JpaSubQuery
